name: DinersDeals
overview:
DinersDeals.Com is a Group Buying, Daily Restaurant Deal platform for diners in cities across the United States and Canada.

DinersDeals.Com allows members and subscribers to save 40% to 90% on cuisines raging from African, American, Asian, Bar/Lounge, Barbecue, Brazilian, Caribbean, Chinese, Continental Creole/Cajun, European, Fondue, French, German, Greek, Indian, International, Italian, Japanese, Latin/Spanish, Mexican, Middle Eastern, Seafood, South American, Steak, Sushi, Thai and Vegetarian.

The platform also allows the meal deal buyers to make table reservations when buying the deals. This enables them to avoid waiting on line when redeeming their vouchers, while at the same time allowing the restaurants to know the number of deal buyers coming to redeem their vouchers on a given day.

DinersDeals.Com is located in Atlanta, Georgia.
